{
  "stem": "27335.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did American plane, because there was the Americans, the British, the French, and the Soviets military commission there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we did American plane.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They flew us-- flew us back to-- back to Bari in Italy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From there, they flew us back not there enough, into Siena, an ancient, ancient Italian town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There we spent, I don't know, 10, 11 days or something, or maybe-- maybe more.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then finally we got our order, and we took a train down to Naples.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a British ship there waiting, waiting for-- there was some Canadian troops there who-- who were the rear guards, because the Canadians fought there in earlier years.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we came back to-- back to England.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then they discharged me, and my [INAUDIBLE] was with me from the British Secret Service there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then on a-- I forget the name of the ship that they-- we sailed back to Canada, and here I got my--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--My discharge paper from the Canadian Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, not in Budapest, because when I separated from Mrs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Szenes-- Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tigany, that was the-- from the doctor's wife, I heard when I was in the other room, when she was telling to Mrs.-- Mrs.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tigany, this doctor's wife, that Therese-- Therese?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, her name was also Therese.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I heard that Hannah Szenes is back in the country.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Gee, I got a shock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I wasn't sure because Szenes is so common name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wasn't so sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But only-- only years after I got a Hungarian-- a Hungarian language book from Israel, from-- from Joe [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Gershman, ?] the editor of [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Wochenblatt. ?] He got it from somebody from Israel, this Hungarian book, and we were printing in the same print shop in Toronto here.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
